                   double vph,
                   double vsv,
                   double vsh,
                   double eta,
                   boolean isDisc)
        Create a (possibly) anisotropic model sample and it's isotropic equivalent.
        Parameters:
        r - Radius in kilometers
        vpv - Vertically polarized P velocity in kilometers/second
        vph - Horizontally polarized P velocity in kilometers/second
        vsv - Vertically polarized S velocity in kilometers/second
        vsh - Horizontally polarized S velocity in kilometers/second
        eta - Anisotropy parameter
        isDisc - True if this sample is at a discontinuity
